china 's rapes crop damag by storm the yield on 46,000 hectar ( ha ) of rapes in central china will be cut by up to 70 pct by hailstorm and tornado that swept across nearli 100,000 ha of crop on march 6 , the new china news agenc said today . the storm , which lash the huai and yangtz river and eastern anhui provinc , left two peopl dead and 800 other injur . some 800 hou were flatten and 19 boat sunk , it said . the anhui provinci govern ha sent emerg relief to the 19 counti affect , the news agenc said .